            <div class="slide-title">
              <p>Why Should We Care About Solar Flares?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="slide-content content3">
              <br/>
              <h2>Solar flares ...</h2>
              <br/>
              <ul> 
                <li>Have the ability to disrupt short-wave radio communications due to long lasting radiation storms in the Earth's ionosphere.</li>
                <li>Can create radiation hazards for spaceships and astronauts not protected by the Earth's atmosphere.</li>
                <li>Create solar winds that increase drag on earth's orbitting satelites.</li>
                <li>Are responsible for creating the amazing Aurora Borealis and Aurora Australis.</li>
                <li>Sometimes produce coronal mass ejections</li>
              </ul>
              <div style="margin-left: 3px;">
            <%= link_to image_tag("aurora1-thumb.jpg", :id => "below-gallery", :class=>"media-in-slide aurora-image"),
              '/images/aurora1.jpg', :rel => "prettyPhoto[aurora]", :title => "Aurora Borealis seen from the international space station."%>
              <%= image_tag("aurora1.jpg", :class => "earthquake_screen") %>
            <%= link_to image_tag("aurora3-thumb.jpg", :id => "below-gallery", :class=>"media-in-slide aurora-image"),
              '/images/aurora3.jpg', :rel => "prettyPhoto[aurora]", :title => "Aurora Borealis in Alaska."%>
              <%= image_tag("aurora3.jpg", :class => "earthquake_screen") %>
            <%= link_to image_tag("aurora2-thumb.jpg", :id => "below-gallery", :class=>"media-in-slide aurora-image"),
              '/images/aurora2.jpg', :rel => "prettyPhoto[aurora]", :title => "Aurora Borealis from Spacelab 3"%>
